##  Lessons Learned While Updating

- I noticed a few things hadnâ€™t been logged during implementation. For example, I had forgotten to document the **CloudTrail log validation** feature â€” fixing that now strengthens our audit trail.  
- Realizing I had no formal version tracking for changes made to the SSP. Going forward, Iâ€™ll adopt a **changelog approach** to track what was modified and when.  
- This work will significantly streamline the **Assess phase** when external reviewers ask, â€œShow me how you implemented that control.â€ The answers are now at my fingertips.

> A well-documented SSP tells a story â€” not just of controls, but of **intentional design**, **risk-informed choices**, and **continuous improvement**.

